ent Product and Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/michaelbud\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc46d3581cd1b084b848e675b2c5f216?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc46d3581cd1b084b848e675b2c5f216?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/michaelbud\" class=\"reviewer-name\"> <small>(michaelbud)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">June 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The Events Calendar is an amazing product, but beyond that, their support team is stellar.  I was having a problem with compatibility with another plugin (OxygenBuilder) and although they don\'t support integration with other plugins they were able to provide me with detailed information and support to help me resolve the conflict.\n\nBRAVO!  They have gone above and beyond!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Uninstalled within an hour</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/robbielokeoys\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1960184170a4b1e84bc1ccda9ce0b0bb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1960184170a4b1e84bc1ccda9ce0b0bb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/robbielokeoys\" class=\"reviewer-name\">robbielokeoys</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">June 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I was looking for just a simple plugin to show visitors some events in a calendar format, this plugin came with a gigantic boatload of nonsense with a billion settings and options to do things I just don\'t need to do, and it wouldn\'t show the one event I attempted to display.\n\nThe simple act of adding an event, time and date etc, is so convoluted I couldn\'t work out how to do it so that something actually displays in the calendar (the link for which I stumbled across while angrily attempting to work out how to use this plugin).\n\nThe basic function of a calendar wouldn\'t work no matter how much I tried, and the information to fix this was non-existent.\n\nIf you want a massive plugin with a billion things you don\'t need or want, and one that apparently doesn\'t do its most basic function with any kind of simplicity or ease, then waste your time with this one for an hour before going with something far better. Or, just heed my warning and skip this one for something else.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Super plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chartkamp\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1cd36183ea5e46279fdcd6f36c99da9d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1cd36183ea5e46279fdcd6f36c99da9d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chartkamp\" class=\"reviewer-name\">chartkamp</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">June 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I used it for years, now I install it again on a new website.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Helps but it is a little bit expensive</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cristianoamerixo\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a7bbd193530a63ab7a31737e4f3d1958?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a7bbd193530a63ab7a31737e4f3d1958?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cristianoamerixo\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cristianoamerixo</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">June 22, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The plugin is great, the features I need are really expensive </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Expensive or without shortcodes</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pqinstitute\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/585f6bce8041173abfd156d781caf41e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/585f6bce8041173abfd156d781caf41e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pqinstitute\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pqinstitute</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">June 22, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It\'s not a bad calendar, but it could be a lot better. You will not use it anywhere in the free version as the shortcode option is reserved for the paid version. If you want to have a fully functional calendar you need to buy a bundle package - the problem is that the packages are constructed in such a way that it is very unprofitable and expensive. It also turns out that translation is not possible in 100%. Part of the menu is untranslatable in Loco or Poedit and you have to look for information that you won\'t find anywhere. Do not count on help.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">issues between iPhone vs PC (in dev)</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tvsmvp\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af95a449e8ed9e31a5ead06155f39a55?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af95a449e8ed9e31a5ead06155f39a55?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tvsmvp\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tvsmvp</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">June 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Changes made on the \"Events Template Settings\" page are seen on iphones - no changes noted on a pc running Chrome. It\'s like I\'ve got two sites...</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">No support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lzevon\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3f24a1071f5b51db77c4bf7e54cd2ce7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3f24a1071f5b51db77c4bf7e54cd2ce7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lzevon\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lzevon</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">June 11, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve used both the free and paid versions of this plugin and support is always an issue. If you\'re expecting to hear back from your plugin developer or their support team find another calendar plugin. I\'m logged into theeventscalendar.com and need to login (again) to support but have been unable to do so. Questions on the forum go unanswered. Very frustrating.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Content</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star