"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin. Thanks!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quintinoapp\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/639ca3227fa07c573238cd917cf29e79?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/639ca3227fa07c573238cd917cf29e79?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quintinoapp\" class=\"reviewer-name\">quintinoapp</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">May 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is really great plugin with really nice functionality. Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Absolutely atrocious!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sanch3x\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a5d04cb72f2f263f8263e087a8d2bc55?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a5d04cb72f2f263f8263e087a8d2bc55?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sanch3x\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sanch3x</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 10, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Of all the plugins that have gained some traction on WP.org, this is by far the worst. We\'ve bought some of their premium plugins thinking they\'d solve some issues but it only piles on some more. They claim they\'ll fix issues but months go by with no movement. Avoid any product by Modern Tribe -- their calendar is just as bad (if not worse) than this one.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very frequent updates</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/roabe\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1eb704cbbb85d93328512ce248cbf8a2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1eb704cbbb85d93328512ce248cbf8a2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/roabe\" class=\"reviewer-name\">roabe</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 4, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very frequent updates, it\'s not comfortable... Is this a bad product perhaps? Wouldn\'t it be enough once or twice a year? That\'s not good.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thank you so much!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/piiather\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8101367ef737c6e88aaf38449a6ee3f9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8101367ef737c6e88aaf38449a6ee3f9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/piiather\" class=\"reviewer-name\">piiather</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">March 31, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Really nice plugin with absolutely clean and simple ideology. It\'s didn\'t take too much time to configure it. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Cool plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mobrock\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9105b8a0b2f8f9898657a6e0b7b1a4da?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9105b8a0b2f8f9898657a6e0b7b1a4da?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mobrock\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mobrock</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">March 1, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Plugin is really nice and simple in use. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Failed in basic funtionallities</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atanai\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08d5c32a439271fd0b7f360da0d58827?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/08d5c32a439271fd0b7f360da0d58827?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atanai\" class=\"reviewer-name\">atanai</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">February 25, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Unfortunately, my experience with this plugin was bad.\n\n. Basic functionality failed with the theme I choose\n. Basic functionality failed in Microsoft Edge\n\nThe support seems to be responsive, but it cost me so much time of working and more time to perform the tests on my site that I decided to ask for a refund and look for another solution.\n\nI do not recommend at this moment this plugin.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Had to roll back recent upgrades</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cragsdell\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a8df66197fdcf0e32627a6bee7f93f40?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a8df66197fdcf0e32627a6bee7f93f40?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cragsdell\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cragsdell<